OL,3,C'Iconic voice': Tributes paid as
OL,4,CGladiators referee John Anderson dies
OL,5,Caged 92
OL,7,FGladiators referee John Anderson has
OL,8,Fdied aged 92, the TV show said.
OL,10,FThe Scottish sports coach was best
OL,11,Fknown for his role as the umpire in
OL,12,Fthe original ITV show, between 1992
OL,13,Fand 2000, and the revamped short-lived
OL,14,FSky series.
OL,16,FHe also trained more than 100
OL,17,FOlympians, and was inducted into the
OL,18,FCoaching Hall of Fame in 2002.
