OL,3,C'Iconic voice': Tributes paid as
OL,4,CGladiators referee John Anderson dies
OL,5,Caged 92
OL,7,FOn Instagram, the official account for
OL,8,FGladiators shared a statement saying:
OL,9,F"We are deeply saddened to hear of the
OL,10,Fpassing of our beloved referee, John
OL,11,FAnderson, at the age of 92.
OL,13,F"Our hearts go out to his friends and
OL,14,Ffamily. John will forever be
OL,15,Fremembered as the iconic voice that
OL,16,Fbrought us 'Gladiators Ready!
OL,17,FContenders Ready!'."
OL,19,FHe would follow the introduction with
OL,20,Fa countdown, saying: "Three, two, one."
