OL,7,FThe referee in the current BBC show
OL,8,Fwhich began earlier this year, Mark
OL,9,FClattenburg, said: "One of the most
OL,10,Ficonic voices and will always be
OL,11,Fremembered.
OL,13,F"I had the most difficult task to
OL,14,Ffollow him in the new series of
OL,15,FGladiators and watching him keep the
OL,16,FGladiators within the rules will
OL,17,Falways be with me!! Rest in peace
OL,18,Flegend!!"
