OL,3,C'Iconic voice': Tributes paid as
OL,4,CGladiators referee John Anderson dies
OL,5,Caged 92
OL,7,FAnderson was also the head coach for
OL,8,Fthe Amateur Athletics Association of
OL,9,FEngland and Scottish national coach.
OL,11,FHe worked with Staffordshire-born race
OL,12,Fwalker Lisa Kehler, Scottish Olympic
OL,13,Frunner Liz McColgan and hurdler
OL,14,FWilliam Sharman.
OL,16,FOlympic sprinter Jennifer Stoute, who
OL,17,Fwas known as Rebel on Gladiators,
OL,18,Fwrote: "He was the best. He knew how
OL,19,Fto make us laugh and get mad toooo.
OL,20,FBest memories."
